{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master unique abilities and overcome ever-evolving challenges in this anime-inspired pixel-art platformer. Each level introduces new mechanics, intense action, and story-driven twists that pull you deeper into the adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513590/extras/animues_right.png?t=1740070860\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udd79\ufe0f <strong>Unique Gameplay Mechanics</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gravity Control</strong> \u2013 Flip gravity to navigate challenging obstacles and uncover hidden paths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513590/extras/Time_SlowDown.png?t=1740070860\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Time Slowdown</strong> \u2013 Struggling with a difficult level? Unlock the ability to slow down time and turn the odds in your favor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513590/extras/Dual_Play.png?t=1740070860\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dual Character Play</strong> \u2013 In certain levels, take control of two characters simultaneously, solving puzzles and overcoming obstacles together.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udd25 <strong>Thrilling Boss Fights</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513590/extras/Boss_Fight.png?t=1740070860\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Escape &amp; Outsmart</strong> \u2013 Some bosses can\u2019t be defeated by brute force. Use your wits to escape and outmaneuver them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513590/extras/boss_shooting.png?t=1740070860\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>High-Intensity Shootouts</strong> \u2013 Face off against powerful enemies in adrenaline-fueled battles that require precision and strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513590/extras/company.png?t=1740070860\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfad <strong>A Story-Driven Experience</strong><br>Every challenge is woven into the narrative, drawing you deeper into the world and its mysteries. Experience intense plot twists, build bonds with unforgettable characters, and discover the secrets that shape your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you ready to take on this journey?</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3513590?t=1740070860","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513590/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740070860","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513590/ddb70f7c083100ca88164bf09dbbe46cc3ce4c0a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740070860","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513590/ddb70f7c083100ca88164bf09dbbe46cc3ce4c0a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740070860","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master unique abilities and overcome ever-evolving challenges in this anime-inspired pixel-art platformer. Each level introduces new mechanics, intense action, and story-driven twists that pull you deeper into the adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3513590/extras/animues_right.png?t=1740070860\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\